								p After spending more than 15 years in technology supporting Retail and Logistics sectors throughout North America, Chad joins NAI Ohio Equities to continue his passion for helping others achieve their goals through Commercial Real Estate.  As a Retail small business owner and real estate investor, Chad has years of experience as both a landlord and commercial tenant, which lead to his career in Commercial Real Estate.  He continues to use his passion assisting others to achieve their financial goals through Real Estate.  Chad has lived in Columbus, OH nearly his entire life!  He is married with two beautiful daughters.
