								p I was born and raised in Columbus, having graduated from Hilliard Davidson High School.  After graduating from Ohio University, I knew I wanted to be in Columbus long term. Columbus offers a thriving arts and cultural scene with numerous museums, theaters, sporting events, and festivals throughout the year. I love the balance between urban amenities and the suburban feel that Columbus offers.  
